      "keywords": ["Greenskin", "Greenskins", "Orc", "Orcs", "Goblin", "Goblins", "Snotling", "Snotlings", "Cave Squig", "Squig", "Squigs"],
      "description": "Pea-brained creatures akin to enthusiastic, uncontrolled puppies, Snotlings are scavengers and natural mimics, picking up bones and shiny things wherever they go, or copying the actions of anything they see. If pushed into conflict by Goblins or Orcs, they fight in stinking swarms, trying to overwhelm their foes through sheer weight of numbers. To do this they find all sorts of disgusting and noxious substances, like poisonous fungus and bodily waste, to hurl at their enemies.",
