      "description": "Bethilda's husband was slaughtered by Beastmen raiding the village of Reikherz. Four months later, she was evicted for failing to pay rent. Desperate, Bethilda approached her cousin, Alwin, a wanted outlaw. After a little persuasion, Bethilda joined his band of brigands harassing the Karstadt–Siedlung road and was surprised by just how exhilarating she found highway robbery. Now she rides as Black Bella and has built a reputation for brutal ruthlessness that now concerns her cousin deeply.",
