  "name": "Skeleton",
  "faction": "Restless Dead",
  "description": "Skeletons are the fleshless bones of those long dead, reanimated by dark magic to walk the earth as mockeries of the living. Those who died and were not laid to rest according to the rituals of Morr, the God of Death, may be resurrected in this form by a sufficiently powerful necromancer. Utterly mindless, Skeletons will fight until their bones are smashed to pieces. They have no courage for they have no fear. They cannot be killed because they are not alive.",
